# Released artifacts and generated registry JSON are byte-addressed content —
# their sha256 digests are recorded in registry/blocks/*.json and verified by
# every `ion-drive add`. Disable EOL translation so a Windows checkout serves
# (and `registry build --check` hashes) exactly the committed bytes.
*/dist/** -text
registry/** -text
schemas/** -text
registries.json -text
registry.config.json -text
